\c 3
\s Amadodana kaAroni
\p
\v 1 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zikaAroni lezikaMozisi, ngosuku iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakhuluma ngalo loMozisi entabeni yeSinayi.
\v 2 Lala ngamabizo amadodana kaAroni; izibulo uNadabi, loAbihu, uEleyazare, loIthamari\x + Eks. 6.23.\x*.
\v 3 La ngamabizo amadodana kaAroni, abapristi abagcotshiweyo, owabehlukanisela ukusebenza njengabapristi\x + Levi 8.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uNadabi loAbihu bafa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho benikela umlilo ongejwayelekanga phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* enkangala yeSinayi\x + Levi 10.1,2; Nani 26.61; 1 Lan. 24.2.\x*. Babengelabantwana. Ngakho uEleyazare loIthamari basebenza njengabapristi phambi kukaAroni uyise.
\p
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 6 Sondeza isizwe sakoLevi, usimise phambi kukaAroni umpristi, ukuthi bamsebenzele\x + 1.50; 8.6; 18.2.\x*.
\v 7 Bazagcina imfanelo yakhe lemfanelo yenhlangano yonke phambi kwethente lenhlangano ukwenza inkonzo yethabhanekele.
\v 8 Bazalondoloza yonke impahla yethente lenhlangano, lemfanelo yabantwana bakoIsrayeli, ukuthi benze inkonzo yethabhanekele\x + 3.38; 8.11,15,24,26.\x*.
\v 9 Njalo uzanikela amaLevi kuAroni lemadodaneni akhe; aphiwe lokuphiwa kuye bephuma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 8.19; 18.6.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe uzabamisa, bagcine-ke ubupristi babo\x + 18.7.\x*. Lowemzini osondelayo uzabulawa\x + 3.38; 1.51.\x*.
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 12 Mina-ke, khangela, ngithethe amaLevi ephuma phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli endaweni yalo lonke izibulo elivula isizalo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli. Ngakho amaLevi azakuba ngawami\x + 8.16; 3.41.\x*,
\v 13 ngoba lonke izibulo lingelami\x + Eks. 13.2. Levi 27.26. Nani 8.16. Luka 2.23.\x* ngosuku engatshaya ngalo lonke izibulo elizweni leGibhithe. Ngizehlukanisele lonke izibulo koIsrayeli, kusukela emuntwini kusiya enyamazaneni; lizakuba ngelami\x + Eks. 13.12,15; Nani 8.17.\x*; ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi enkangala yeSinayi isithi:
\v 15 Bala abantwana bakoLevi ngezindlu zaboyise langensendo zabo; wonke owesilisa kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, uzababala\x + 3.39; 26.62; 1.47.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho uMozisi wababala ngokomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd* njengokulaywa kwakhe.
\v 17 Lala ayengamadodana kaLevi ngamabizo awo: UGerishoni loKohathi loMerari\x + Gen. 46.11. Eks. 6.16; Nani 26.57. 1 Lan. 6.1,16; 23.6.\x*.
\v 18 Lala ngamabizo amadodana kaGerishoni ngensendo zawo: ULibini loShimeyi\x + Eks. 6.17; 1 Lan. 6.17; 23.7.\x*.
\v 19 Lamadodana kaKohathi ngensendo zawo: UAmramu loIzihari, uHebroni loUziyeli\x + Eks. 6.18; 1 Lan. 6.2,18.\x*.
\v 20 Lamadodana kaMerari ngensendo zawo: UMahli loMushi\x + Eks. 6.19; 1 Lan. 6.19; 23.21.\x*. Lezi zinsendo zamaLevi ngezindlu zaboyise.
\p
\v 21 KuGerishoni kwakulosendo lwamaLibini losendo lwamaShimeyi; lezi zinsendo zamaGerishoni.
\v 22 Ababalwayo babo, ngenani labo bonke abesilisa, kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, ababalwayo babo babeyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lamakhulu amahlanu.
\v 23 Insendo zamaGerishoni zizamisa amathente azo ngemva kwethabhanekele ngentshonalanga\x + 1.53; 3.29,35,38.\x*.
\v 24 Lesiphathamandla sendlu kayise wamaGerishoni sizakuba nguEliyasafi indodana kaLayeli.
\v 25 Lemfanelo yamadodana kaGerishoni ethenteni lenhlangano izakuba\x + 4.24-26.\x* lithabhanekele\x + Eks. 25.9.\x*, lethente\x + Eks. 26.7; 36.14.\x*, isifulelo salo\x + Eks. 26.14.\x*, lesilenge somnyango wethente lenhlangano,
\v 26 lamakhetheni eguma\x + Eks. 27.9.\x*, lesilenge somnyango weguma elingasethabhanekeleni lelingaselathini inhlangothi zonke\x + Eks. 27.16.\x*, lentambo zalo, ngokomsebenzi walo wonke\x + 3.37. Eks. 35.18; 39.40.\x*.
\p
\v 27 LakuKohathi kwakulosendo lwamaAmramu, losendo lwamaIzihari, losendo lwamaHebroni, losendo lwamaUziyeli. Lezi zinsendo zamaKohathi\x + 1 Lan. 26.23.\x*.
\v 28 Kunani labo bonke abesilisa, kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, babeyizinkulungwane eziyisificaminwembili lamakhulu ayisithupha, begcina imfanelo yendlu engcwele.
\v 29 Insendo zamadodana kaKohathi zizamisa amathente azo eceleni kwethabhanekele ngeningizimu\x + Eks. 40.22,24; Nani 3.35.\x*.
\v 30 Lesiphathamandla sendlu kayise wensendo zamaKohathi sizakuba nguElizafani indodana kaUziyeli\x + Eks. 6.22. Levi 10.4.\x*.
\v 31 Lemfanelo yawo izakuba ngumtshokotsho\x + Eks. 25.10.\x*, letafula\x + Eks. 25.23.\x*, loluthi lwesibane\x + Eks. 25.31.\x*, lamalathi\x + Eks. 27.1; 30.1.\x*, lezitsha zendlu engcwele abakhonza ngazo, lesilenge\x + Eks. 35.12; 39.34; 40.21; Eks. 26.31; Nani 4.5.\x*, layo yonke inkonzo yalo.
\v 32 Njalo umphathi weziphathamandla zamaLevi uzakuba nguEleyazare, indodana kaAroni umpristi; ubuphathi \add bakhe\add* babukwabagcina ukulindwa kwendlu engcwele.
\p
\v 33 KoMerari kwakulusendo lwamaMahli losendo lwamaMushi; lezi zinsendo zamaMerari.
\v 34 Lababalwayo babo, ngenani labo bonke abesilisa, kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, babeyizinkulungwane eziyisithupha lamakhulu amabili.
\v 35 Lesiphathamandla sendlu kayise wensendo zakoMerari sizakuba nguZuriyeli indodana kaAbihayili. Bazamisa amathente abo eceleni kwethabhanekele ngenyakatho.
\v 36 Lobuphathi bokulinda bamadodana kaMerari buzakuba ngamapulanka ethabhanekele\x + Eks. 26.15.\x*, lemithando yalo\x + Eks. 26.26.\x*, lensika zalo\x + Eks. 26.32,37.\x*, lezisekelo zalo\x + Eks. 26.19.\x*, lezitsha zalo zonke, lawo wonke umsebenzi walo,
\v 37 lensika zeguma inhlangothi zonke, lezisekelo zazo\x + Eks. 27.10.\x*, lezikhonkwane zazo\x + Eks. 27.19.\x*, lentambo zazo\x + 3.26.\x*.
\p
\v 38 Lalabo ababemise amathente abo phambi kwethabhanekele ngempumalanga, phambi kwethente lenhlangano, kwakungoMozisi loAroni lamadodana akhe, belondoloza ukulindwa kwendlu engcwele, kusenzelwa umlindo wabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 1.53.\x*. Lowemzini osondelayo uzabulawa\x + 3.10.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Bonke ababalwayo bamaLevi, oMozisi loAroni abababalayo, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*, ngezinsapho zabo, bonke abesilisa kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili\x + 3.22,28,34; Nani 3.46-49.\x*.
\s Uhlengo lwamazibulo
\p
\v 40 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Bala wonke amazibulo esilisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli, kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, uthathe inani lamabizo abo.
\v 41 Uzangithathela amaLevi (ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*) endaweni yawo wonke amazibulo phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli; lezifuyo zamaLevi endaweni yamazibulo wonke phakathi kwezifuyo zabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 3.12,45.\x*.
\v 42 Ngakho uMozisi wabala wonke amazibulo phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuye.
\v 43 Lawo wonke amazibulo esilisa, ngenani lamabizo, kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu, kwababaliweyo babo, ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lantathu.
\p
\v 44 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 45 Thatha amaLevi endaweni yamazibulo wonke phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, lezifuyo zamaLevi endaweni yezifuyo zabo; lamaLevi azakuba ngawami\x + 3.12,41.\x*; ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 46 Mayelana labazahlengwa, abangamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lantathu bamazibulo abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 13.13; Nani 18.15.\x*, abaphezu kwenani lamaLevi\x + 3.39,43.\x*;
\v 47 uzathatha \w lamashekeli\w** nganhlanu nganhlanu ngekhanda\x + Levi 27.6. Nani 18.16.\x*, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele uzawathatha\x + 1.2.\x*; ishekeli \w lingamagera\w** angamatshumi amabili\x + Eks. 30.13.\x*.
\v 48 Unike kuAroni lakumadodana akhe imali yabahlengiweyo abasele phakathi kwabo.
\v 49 UMozisi wasethatha imali yohlengo kulabo ababesele phezu kwabahlengwa ngamaLevi.
\v 50 Wayithatha imali kumazibulo abantwana bakoIsrayeli, \add amashekeli\add* ayinkulungwane lamakhulu amathathu lamatshumi ayisithupha lanhlanu, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + 3.46,47.\x*.
\v 51 UMozisi wasenika uAroni lamadodana akhe imali yabahlengiweyo, ngokomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd*, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* imlayile uMozisi\x + 3.48.\x*.